name: Deluxe Wireless Noise-Canceling Headphones
description: Premium over-ear headphones with advanced noise-canceling technology, Bluetooth 5.0 connectivity, 30-hour battery life, and comfortable memory foam ear cushions. Perfect for audiophiles and frequent travelers seeking high-quality sound and immersive listening experience.

name: Smart Home Security Camera System
description: 4K Ultra HD wireless security camera with night vision, motion detection, two-way audio, and cloud storage. Includes mobile app for real-time monitoring and alerts. Weather-resistant design suitable for indoor and outdoor use.

name: Ergonomic Office Chair with Lumbar Support
description: Adjustable ergonomic office chair with breathable mesh back, lumbar support, 4D armrests, and multi-position tilt mechanism. Designed for maximum comfort during long working hours with premium quality materials and durability.

name: Portable Bluetooth Speaker with LED Lights
description: Waterproof portable Bluetooth speaker with 360-degree sound, powerful bass, RGB LED light show, and 12-hour battery life. Perfect for outdoor parties, beach trips, and camping adventures. Supports multiple device connectivity.

name: Smart Robot Vacuum Cleaner
description: Advanced robot vacuum with laser navigation, multi-floor mapping, powerful suction, and app control. Features automatic recharging, virtual wall technology, and compatible with voice assistants. Ideal for pet owners and busy households.

name: Professional Digital Camera Kit
description: Full-frame mirrorless digital camera with 4K video recording, 24.2MP sensor, interchangeable lens, and professional-grade image stabilization. Kit includes extra battery, memory card, and carrying case for photographers and enthusiasts.

name: Compact Air Purifier with HEPA Filter
description: Medical-grade HEPA air purifier with activated carbon filter, removes 99.97% of airborne particles, allergens, and pollutants. Quiet operation, three-speed settings, and compact design suitable for bedrooms, offices, and small spaces.

name: Smart Fitness Tracker Watch
description: Advanced fitness smartwatch with heart rate monitoring, GPS tracking, sleep analysis, waterproof design, and multi-sport modes. Includes color touchscreen, smartphone notifications, and long battery life for active lifestyles.

name: Electric Standing Desk with Memory Settings
description: Height-adjustable electric standing desk with smooth motor, memory preset positions, sturdy steel frame, and large workspace. Includes cable management tray and compatible with multiple monitor setups for ergonomic home and office use.

name: Portable Power Station with Solar Charging
description: High-capacity portable power station with solar charging capability, multiple output ports (AC, USB, USB-C), pure sine wave inverter, and rugged design. Perfect for camping, outdoor adventures, and emergency backup power.

name: Smart WiFi Enabled Coffee Maker
description: Programmable WiFi coffee maker with smartphone app control, built-in grinder, thermal carafe, and multiple brewing options. Features voice assistant compatibility, custom strength settings, and automatic scheduling.

name: Wireless Gaming Mouse with RGB Lighting
description: High-precision wireless gaming mouse with adjustable DPI, ergonomic design, customizable RGB lighting, and long-lasting battery. Includes programmable buttons and compatible with multiple gaming platforms and devices.

name: Noise-Reducing Wireless Earbuds
description: True wireless earbuds with active noise cancellation, touch controls, sweatproof design, and 8-hour battery life. Includes charging case, multiple ear tip sizes, and high-quality sound for music and calls.

name: Smart Indoor Herb Garden Kit
description: Automated indoor herb garden with LED grow lights, water reservoir, and seed pod system. Includes multiple herb seed varieties, nutrient solutions, and smartphone app for monitoring plant growth and health.

name: 4K Ultra HD Smart Television
description: 55-inch 4K Ultra HD Smart TV with HDR, wide color gamut, built-in streaming apps, voice control, and thin bezel design. Features multiple HDMI ports, low input lag for gaming, and advanced picture processing technology.

name: Compact Multi-Function Blender
description: High-power blender with multiple attachments for smoothies, food processing, and personal cups. Features stainless steel blades, variable speed settings, and dishwasher-safe components for easy cleaning.

name: Smart Home Climate Control Thermostat
description: WiFi-enabled smart thermostat with learning capabilities, energy-saving mode, and smartphone app control. Features room sensor compatibility, voice assistant integration, and detailed energy consumption reports.

name: Portable Laptop Cooling Pad
description: Ergonomic laptop cooling pad with multiple fan speeds, adjustable height, and quiet operation. Compatible with laptops 12-17 inches, includes USB-powered cooling, non-slip surface, and LED indicators.

name: High-Performance Wireless Router
description: Dual-band WiFi 6 wireless router with high-speed connectivity, extended range, and multiple device support. Features advanced security protocols, parental controls, and easy mesh system expansion.

name: Smart Digital Picture Frame
description: WiFi-enabled digital photo frame with high-resolution display, cloud storage, and smartphone app for easy photo sharing. Includes motion sensors, automatic slideshow, and touchscreen interface.

name: Portable Solar Power Bank
description: High-capacity solar power bank with fast charging, multiple output ports, rugged waterproof design, and built-in LED flashlight. Perfect for outdoor activities, emergency backup, and travel.

name: Smart Robotic Window Cleaner
description: Automated window cleaning robot with advanced navigation, powerful suction, and safety tether. Works on various glass surfaces, includes remote control, and multiple cleaning modes for efficient window maintenance.

name: Professional Electric Toothbrush Set
description: Advanced electric toothbrush with multiple cleaning modes, pressure sensor, long battery life, and UV sanitizing charging base. Includes multiple brush heads, travel case, and smartphone app tracking.

name: Wireless Charging Desk Lamp
description: Modern LED desk lamp with integrated wireless charging pad, adjustable brightness, color temperature control, and USB charging port. Sleek design suitable for home office and workspace environments.

name: Smart Fitness Mirror Workout System
description: Interactive fitness mirror with live and on-demand workout classes, real-time performance tracking, and personalized training recommendations. Features large HD display, multiple fitness genres, and compact wall-mountable design.
